Posts.Content: Nov 8, 2016 05:15PM Wendyohms wrote: hi jamiens, I also had a high oncotype score of 50. It totally freaked me out and I still can get upset about it. I finished chemo august 3 of this year and rads last month. My attitude is is that the score is to let us know who would benefit most from chemo and you and I fall into that category. We have to have faith that the chemo wipes out all those little buggers and the Amiridex in my case will keep them away. I feel your fear and identify with it. It's definitely one day at a time
Posts.Title: Hi. I'm new. My oncotype is freaking me out. jamiens Warrior4sararyan
